data.text:
Listen to this article!

Tudela is a city in Buena Vista County, Bloxburg Valley, Robloxia. Tudela is located in the Paradise Valley.

Fun Facts[]

The Tudela area was situated along a trade route used by Native Bloxmericans.

Tudela is a young city with nearly 1/3rd of its population under the age of 18. 38% of Tudela’s adults have less than a high school degree, and only 17% have college degrees.

Tudela’s population is also highly diverse.

Colleges and Universities[]
